                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17991204-31-off170 t17991204-31-cd171"></join>, a pair of men's leather shoes, value 4s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17991204-31-victim295" type="victimName">
                     Henry 
                     Bell
                  <interp inst="t17991204-31-victim295" type="surname" value="Bell"></interp>
